data.description: Full stack web application for Gacha game
data.responsibility: Personal project. Developing a web application to manage Gacha game items and characters. Implemented user authentication, API calls, database management, and responsive design using Tailwind CSS and Next.js. Database managed with Supabase. Currently in development, working MVP features. Working on the frontend at the moment.

data.description: SaaS Tattoo artist discovery and booking management platform.

Full stack website development, design handed off by client. Implementing WordPress theme and customizations. Integrated WooCommerce for e-commerce functionality.
